
Repository from [this blogpost](https://lethain.com/streamlit-llms/).

To install and run on a computer with Python3:


    git clone git@github.com:lethain/llm-explorer.git
    python3 -m venv env
    . ./env/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    streamlit run main.py

Then it will open in your browser automatically.
You'll also need to provide an OpenAI API key
[as specified here](https://github.com/lethain/llm-explorer/blob/main/oai_utils.py).